协作者-云社工；功能介绍：志愿者信息管理、社会工作者信息管理、公益信息发布、社会工作专业交流。
Collaborator - Yun social worker; Function introduction: Volunteer information management, social worker information management, public service information release, social work professional exchange.
本文是协作者在“农民工抗疫救援行动”中，针对困境农民工家庭开展的个案访谈之一，旨在快速识别疫情中的脆弱人群及其需求，为疫情防控和救援工作提供参考，我们整理出来与你分享。
This article is one of the case interviews conducted by the co-authors in the "Anti-epidemic Rescue Operation for Migrant Workers," which aims to identify the vulnerable people and their needs in the epidemic quickly, and to provide reference for prevention, control and rescue work.
疫情下的深呼吸——困境农民工家庭个案实录（五）我们也不知道该怎么办，只能等了口述者：范芸（化名）/河南籍打工所在地：南京编者按：范芸，56岁，患有脑梗、高血压，独自带着9岁的孙女小语在南京生活。
We didn't know what to do, so we had to wait for the dictator: Fan Yun (alias) / Henan's place of work: Nanjing Editor's Note: Fan Yun, 56, suffered from cerebral infarction, hypertension, and lived alone in Nanjing with her 9-year-old granddaughter.
小语的父母在小语9个月大的时候离婚，妈妈离开了家，爸爸常年外出打工。
Whispering parents in whispers 9 months old when the divorce, the mother left home, father year-round work outside.
几年前，范云的丈夫也离家出走，至今未归。
Fan's husband also left home a few years ago and has not returned since.
范云靠在饭店洗盘洗碗的打工钱，以及小语爸爸每月寄来的300元生活费，维持着祖孙两人的生活。
Fan Yun depends on the hotel dishwasher working money, as well as a small voice father sent 300 yuan a month living expenses, maintain the lives of the two grandchildren.
我来南京有9年了，是小语8个月大的时候过来照顾她。
I've been in Nanjing for nine years, and I came to take care of her when I was eight months old.
我的儿子和儿媳（小语爸妈）离婚了，对我儿子影响很大，原本他只是吸烟，但孩子妈妈离开后，他就经常喝酒，半夜不睡觉，出去不回家。
When my son and daughter-in-law divorced, it had a great impact on my son. He used to smoke, but after his mother left, he often drank, stayed up at night and did not go home.
我带着小语去找到他，他会说“妈，你回去吧，我没事”，“妈，你不要管”，时间长了，我也管不了，后面孩子爸爸就去杭州打工，离开了这里……我在一家小餐馆上班，洗碗洗盘子，每个月挣个两千块钱，是私人做的，他让我过去帮个忙，每个月开点工资。
I went to him in a whisper and he would say "Mom, you go back, I'm OK" and "Mom, you don't mind." When the time was long, my father went to Hangzhou for a job and left... I worked in a small restaurant, washing dishes and making 2,000 dollars a month.
今年7月份到期的（合同），但过了年，他没给我打电话，我也没打，不知道还能不能干。
It was due in July this year, but by the end of next year, he hadn't called me, I hadn't called, and I didn't know if he could do it.
我眼睛老花，不带眼镜看不见，腿也不好，走路不太方便，有时候打嗝不舒服就喝白开水，有点高血压，但这些身体毛病都没有去医院检查——说实话，太贵了，不敢去。
My eyes are old, I can't see without glasses, my legs are not good, I don't walk very well, I drink boiled water sometimes with hiccups, I have a little high blood pressure, but I don't go to the hospital for any of these physical ailments - honestly, it's too expensive to go.
▲ 协作者社会工作者探望范芸和小语（拍摄于2019年春季）今年我们没有回老家，好几年没回去了，回一次老家不容易，拖家带口的，一来一回又要花好多钱。
Social workers visit Fan Yun and Xiaoyu (spring 2019) This year we did not go back home, several years did not go home, back home is not easy, Tuxingkou, one time it will cost a lot of money.
关于疫情，是通过协作者你们发的消息了解的，还有微信群里朋友说的，亲朋好友也都发了，说外面都堵起来了，不要出门，周边社区也在手机上发了消息。
About the epidemic, through the co-author of your message, there are also micro-letter group of friends said, relatives and friends have also sent, said that the outside all blocked up, do not go out, the surrounding community also posted on the mobile phone.
现在知道要出去戴口罩，在家里多开窗通风，勤洗手，口罩也会用，戴铁条的地方往鼻子上一按就行了，用几个小时再换，（换下来的）要丢到垃圾桶里。
Now know to wear a mask, open more windows in your home, wash your hands frequently, use a mask, just press the place with the iron bar on your nose, change it in a few hours, and throw it in the trash can.
病毒主要是通过打喷嚏、咳嗽传播的。
Viruses are spread mainly by sneezing or coughing.
得了这个肺炎以后会发烧、胸闷、浑身酸痛，要及时到医院去查。
After getting this pneumonia will have a fever, chest tightness, aching all over, to the hospital in time to check.
家里有一二十个一次性口罩，消毒水没有，以前在超市买，5块钱1包。
The family has a dozen disposable masks, disinfectant water, previously bought in the supermarket, 5 yuan a bag.
昨天我想再买几个都没有了。
I think I didn't have any more yesterday.
这几天就出过一次门，昨天晚上家里没菜了，去买点菜，我到超市，买的萝卜，3块钱1斤，原来1块钱1斤，翻了好多倍。
I went to the supermarket to buy radishes, three yuan a catty, originally one dollar a catty, has multiplied many times.
现在这个肺炎，我挺害怕的，因为这个病太严重了。
Now this pneumonia, I am quite afraid, because this illness is too serious.
“非典”那时候我还在老家，孩子都还小，那个时候还都没手机，就村里面讲“非典”来了，都不要出门，也都呆在家里，那时候没有口罩，就门口弄点石灰撒到屋里面消消毒，床下撒撒。
When I was back home and the children were still young, I didn't have a cell phone, so I said "SARS" came from the village. I stayed at home and didn't go out.
那时候关于没有手机，就听人家讲，来了解情况，现在看手机就能看到。
At that time about no cell phone, just listen to people, to understand the situation, now you can see the mobile phone.
▲范芸住的出租屋（拍摄于2019年春季）孩子学校也通知延期开学了，延到2月17号，原来是2月8号的。
Fan Yun's Rental Housing (filmed in the spring of 2019) The children's school has also been postponed to February 17, the original February 8.
学校通知说不要出门，把门窗开开，出门戴口罩，让小孩写作业。
School notice not to go out, open doors and windows, wear masks, let the children write homework.
通知几乎天天发，发了好几天，这两天没让她出门，让她在家里写作业。
The notice was sent almost daily, for several days, and she was not allowed to go out these two days to do her homework at home.
她说，要去后面山上玩，我说外面有病菌，要带口罩不能出去，她懂，就不去了。
She said, to play in the back of the mountains, I said there is germs outside, to wear masks can not go out, she understood, not to go.
我就在家做饭，看看小孩写字，洗个衣服。
I just cook at home, watch kids write, wash clothes.
现在外面都没有人，都不敢出去。
There's nobody out there right now, not daring to go out.
如果疫情一直持续一两个月的时间，对生活的影响就很大了，一家人还要生活，孩子的上学，吃穿都成问题。
If the epidemic continues for a month or two, the impact on life will be enormous, families will have to live, the children's school, eating and clothing problems.
主要是吃的方面，像我们这样，本来工资就少，还有房租、水电费要交……我们也不知道该怎么办，只能等了。
Mainly food, like us, the original salary, rent, utilities have to pay... we do not know what to do, we have to wait.
社会工作者手记访谈中，能感受到范芸对于突如其来的疫情感到害怕，以及为工作，为孩子的学习和每一天的吃穿发愁。
Social workers in the manual interview, can feel Fan Yun for the sudden outbreak of fear, as well as for work, for the children's study and every day eat and wear worry.
家庭支离破碎，只有和孙女相依为命，说起孩子的父母，说起丈夫，无助与心酸，让范芸泣不成声。
Fragmented family, only and granddaughter alone, talking about the children's parents, talking about her husband, helplessness and heartbreak, let Fan Yun broke down.
孙女，在范芸的生活里，既是动力，也是希望。
The granddaughter, in Fan Yun's life, is both the motive and the hope.
服务建议：当下：1．定期跟进家庭近况，给予奶奶和小语心理慰藉和情感上的支持，为家庭提供基本防护和生活物资支持。
Service Advice: 1. Regular follow-up of the family situation, grant Grandma and whispered psychological comfort and emotional support, and provide basic protection and material support to the family.
2.进一步了解孩子的学习、心理等情况，鼓励其参与协作者在线服务；3.了解家庭下一步的生活规划，跟进奶奶复工情况，给予疫情期间相关的劳动保障咨询或就业信息资讯，确保家庭能在疫情期间或结束后，步入正常的生活轨道。
2. To learn more about children's studies, psychology, etc. and encourage them to participate in the authors' online services; 3. To understand the next steps in family life planning, follow-up on Grandma's return to work, and provide relevant labor security consultation or employment information during the epidemic period to ensure that the family can enter into a normal life cycle during or after the outbreak.
长远：1.链接医护志愿者定期为家庭提供健康咨询指导､体检服务和就医资源；2.疫情结束后，继续为小语对接陪伴天使服务，辅导其学习，提升学习成绩，给予心理支持；3.与小语父亲沟通，督促父亲承担起孩子的监护照顾责任；4.继续提供助学救助。
In the long run: 1. Link to health care volunteers to provide regular health counselling, medical check-ups and medical resources for families; 2. Continue to provide counselling and support to the angels after the outbreak, tutoring them in their studies, improving their academic performance and providing psychological support; 3. Communicate with their fathers and urge them to take care of their children;
